modules.description: Handles conversion between JSON schema one-of representations and ATD-compatible variants. Normalizes input data to a consistent format and restores complex structures like lists or strings during decoding. Useful when parsing JSON schemas that use one-of constructs into ATD-defined types with precise variant handling.

Converts JSON schema one-of constructs to ATD variants, normalizing input data and restoring structured values like lists or strings during decoding. Works directly with JSON and ATD-defined variant types. Enables precise handling of schemas where a field must match one of several distinct types.
